column2: SELECT TOP #  nsaid,ra, dec, mag, ((elpetro_absmag_g +.#*(elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r)+.#) - (#*log(#*#*(z/#),#)+#)) as AbsMag, (elpetro_absmag_g +.#*(elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r)+.#) as AppMag, z,(z*#/#) as Distance, elpetro_mass as Mass, elpetro_mets as Metallicity FROM nsatlas WHERE   (#*z/#)<#
